        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37987290/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37987290/" class="">第6页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/qianyanseu/" class=" " title="Lord Spark">Lord Spark</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="37987290">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">
图形工作站是一个特定用途、窄众市场的产品，而硅谷人却也能将它变成一个不小的产业。
</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-06-18 02:43</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>
图形工作站是一个特定用途、窄众市场的产品，而硅谷人却也能将它变成一个不小的产业。
</q></blockquote>
